{"tid":1299480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無玩夢之歷險？面子既重要性","createTime":"2019-07-09T05:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T11:45:46.000Z","uid":197235,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0907858fbfa8cbc911d17ddd4e9a62ce9d4e02","tid":1299480,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2cFLYdk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2cFLYdk.png&h=1ba1d2b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.）每次於一般地圖死亡或時空任務失敗時,會扣減和戰鬥等級相同的面子值<br />\n<br />\n2.）在一般地圖打死高於自己戰鬥等級的怪物,每隻面子+1<br />\n完成任務時,也會提升許多面子值<br />\n<br />\n3.）NPC拉渥有賣面子+100的道具,9萬元<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">《香港社會信用評分系統》假設</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1.）每次反對政府政策或參與社會運動，會因組織心情扣減信用值<br />\n<br />\n2.）每次完成中共/港共任務，你的信用值便會提高<br />\n<br />\n3.）可以送禮比信用評分組織，提高自己信用值"},{"pid":"ccff2891a43e96a7120eb25e01fd6eb16a61a7db","tid":1299480,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:21:38.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fd0ff68fac7640ad973104f172dd8bbb11d56325","tid":1299480,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"信用值高低有咩影響上網查都知"},{"pid":"8c8c6d99d2037bc22c1c6117a3d46fb0953336c9","tid":1299480,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca6d948b0c0d104365ccefb725512743d93ed6e","tid":1299480,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:22:35.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"69b7419bfee7d03b18d37ecd0c1b5f77707b6f6e","tid":1299480,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:22:47.000Z","msg":"我要見律師"},{"pid":"43460806d67c2